一个保健共识；一个保健合意

bilingual.source: We reached a consensus at the meeting.
bilingual.target: 我们在会议上达成了一个共识。

bilingual.source: After discussion, we finally had a consensus.
bilingual.target: 经过讨论，我们终于有了共识。

bilingual.source: The team reached a consensus on the project plan.
bilingual.target: 团队对项目计划达成了共识。

bilingual.source: Consensus among team members is very important.
bilingual.target: 团队成员之间的共识非常重要。

bilingual.source: They did not reach a consensus on this issue.
bilingual.target: 他们在这个问题上没有达成共识。

bilingual.source: The committee members worked hard to achieve a consensus.
bilingual.target: 委员会成员努力达成共识。

bilingual.source: The general consensus is that more funding is needed.
bilingual.target: 普遍的共识是需要更多的资金。

bilingual.source: They reached an important consensus at the summit meeting.
bilingual.target: 他们在峰会上达成了重要共识。

bilingual.source: After hours of discussion, a consensus began to emerge.
bilingual.target: 经过几个小时的讨论，共识开始出现。

bilingual.source: This plan requires everyone's consensus to be implemented.
bilingual.target: 这个计划需要大家的共识才能实施。

list.abstract: consensus是一个英语单词，名词，作名词时意为“一致；舆论；合意”。

exam_freq_info.chinese: 意见一致; 一致同意

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.zh: 意见一致; 一致同意

examination_example.sentence: Unless a broad <highlight>consensus</highlight> can be reached on reforming the international tax system, other nations are likely to follow suit.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 除非就改革国际税收制度达成广泛共识，否则其他国家可能会效仿。

examination_example.sentence: The Organization for Economic Cooperation and Development is working with 131 countries to reach a <highlight>consensus</highlight> by the end of 2020 on an international solution.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 经济合作与发展组织正在与131个国家合作，以在2020年底前就国际解决方案达成共识。

examination_example.sentence: The emerging <highlight>consensus</highlight> around the bill is a sign that legislators are getting frightened about a politically embarrassing short-term collapse at the USPS.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 围绕该法案正在形成的共识表明，立法者们对美国邮政署在政治上令人尴尬的短期崩溃感到害怕。
